Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希与小步是在极平凡的大阪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,极平凡的阿倍野桥出生的\N少年少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在穿梭在\N另一个世界的阿倍野桥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.56,0:01:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全回不了原来的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这些世界中\N他们必须先打倒的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.80,0:01:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后藉由小鬼的魔力\N才能回到原来的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.27,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么理由嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.31,0:01:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为被极平凡的小学生\N打败的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其魔力也不怎么值得信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.78,0:02:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果他们又穿梭到另一个\N不可思议的世界中了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.44,0:02:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第5话 灭绝！\N阿倍野桥☆古代恐龙商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次来到了恐龙王国了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个\N还有那个全是恐龙哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.43,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎会不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得全被送到你喜欢的世界\N我不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪…\N再胡闹就打你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别打完后才说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.14,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧\N这里的恐龙很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.44,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看侏罗纪的剑龙\N与白垩纪的霸王龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在一起不觉得奇怪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.72,0:03:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此但普通的小学生\N哪会知道的那么详细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.09,0:03:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那个我知道\N是雷龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.06,0:03:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！等等\N确实也有人称它雷龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起\N别打我，别打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.04,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全垒打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前确实有人称它雷龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为掺杂好几只雷龙的化石\N重新拼凑完成的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.85,0:03:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新拼凑完成后\N才慢慢改称为现在的名称的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全长约20公尺\N侏罗纪后期栖息于美洲大陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.76,0:03:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是博学多闻呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是侏罗纪\N到白垩纪时期生物之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管任何问题都难不倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷…萨希教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个年纪还称不上教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.44,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你对喜欢的特殊知识很了解\N但学校的课业却一窍不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.65,0:04:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间内全是恐龙与女生玩的玩偶\N让人觉得很娘娘腔的男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了觉得很恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.99,0:04:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，乖乖\N反正不管我说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不会有人认真听的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是个孤独的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这娃娃很可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经问你好几次这个是什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三犄龙的小孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小三犄龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小恐龙，小恐龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你看见了重要东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有，又没什么特别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.38,0:05:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，如此一来\N我与小步的关系就不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.05,0:06:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不一样的\N会变成仇人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不，该怎么说呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.13,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小东西让我想起了一件事\N它妈妈在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『小东西』让你想到事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『小东西』让你想到什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是谁的小东西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么『小东西』？\N喂！是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是迷路的小恐龙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们就去找它的妈妈吧\N（是什么『小东西』啊？）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里见到的东西都是种缘份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.19,0:06:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当做是日行一善\N世界一家，四海之内皆兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不是人类，是恐龙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.19,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类若四海之内皆兄弟\N或许可将恐龙想成是远房亲戚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么小东西指的是什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你\N例如『小弟弟』啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓一大跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.95,0:07:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这里也是阿倍野桥吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐，还是一样的严肃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.89,0:07:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像问我们有卖鱼吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有卖鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说那边的那个女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.67,0:07:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将你手上抱着的那只红恐龙\N交给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你是这小孩的妈妈吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来眼睛模样还真的有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N连说话语气也很像爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.15,0:08:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是会带来恶运的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由我的占卜所得知的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占卜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我姐姐最喜欢占卜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.49,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天不就是血型.星座.四柱推命\N甚至连动物占卜也考不倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.67,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但结果就只是\N从早到晚都在家占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.70,0:08:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子一天就过去了\N到最后在神桌前睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么搞不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.86,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家人真的非常奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识，我不认识\N（请再多给我一点奖励）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过那种人\N在此他们与我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王，请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连妈妈也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧\N这血肿抓痕就是占卜的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样也是占卜的一种啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这肿起之处很明显的\N就是意味着大地的灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是，还有这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没看到，我什么也没看到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大地被烈火焚烧着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.47,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着！会有红色恐龙出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有人说这不是个\N不祥预兆的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就请报上名来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.24,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴闭嘴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有血缘关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不，先别说这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之那种毫无根据之事\N怎能令人相信呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错\N我们要将她归还给它妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.13,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了一只恐龙\N要让此商店街的人们遭遇不幸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎能只凭肿块就轻率地下决定\N你当我们是傻瓜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.87,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好\N一定会安全送你回到妈妈怀中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.95,0:10:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护将招来毁灭的恐龙者\N下场是…安德鲁西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不交出的话会如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.15,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被判死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是杀生哦\N爷爷没关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可违背女王旨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王的占卜是不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有相信\N每天才能有安全感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使真是如此也绝不能交给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错，反对独裁主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，这小鬼头只是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.69,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此看来\N要抓住他们应该很简单的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别生气，别生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追，给我追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木奈木奈\N托你的福我们才得救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不是木奈木奈\N我叫怪兽王女木奈木奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在名字前\N加上怪兽王女而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.71,0:12:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是女王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怪兽王女！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王女与女王比起来年轻多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个正在进行寻人之旅的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就在这个世界的某处\N但很难碰到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.36,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那果然指的是那个大叔吗？\N在澡堂偷窥的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追上来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:12:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缠的真紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，第一次飞回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果是打到我耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因为飞回来所以人家很高兴嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不是那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是指没打到他们就没意义了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请瞄准点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！又飞回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.47,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N到底是为了什么而投的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N现在不是做那种蠢事的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们好像又追上来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.35,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小犄龙，没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有办法的…\N大概没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为人就是要积极乐观点\N应该不会有问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没路可逃了…\N完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳过去…快…\N大家一起跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…跳得过去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳不过去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合三人之力应该没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫『应该』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接连不断的危机真让人目不暇给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你，这有什么好高兴的\N前方又会是如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…\N前方必定是更大的危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.22,0:14:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样我可是个游泳高手哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我有个淀白鱼的外号吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.42,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大阪湾的海豚呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.03,0:14:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道顿堀的海獭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菖浦池的水鱼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水桶中的昆虫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂里的洗发精？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.48,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为死定了呢！\N萨希，还活着吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.28,0:15:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！但普通情况下准该死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是陨石激烈撞击的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.83,0:15:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从此生物的情况改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人正在找你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你们啊\N到底与我有何关联呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我想问你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔，你会使用魔法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法？我才不会那种低级手法呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:16:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是之前在香港商店街给我们的\N类似低级的符咒帮了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.56,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩，那是最先进的科学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学的符咒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的低级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之既然我们这么有缘\N就告诉你们我的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫优达斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.73,0:16:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的名字\N大概是外国人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但优达斯的脸孔不管怎么看\N都像是个道地的日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，是艺名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N就像查理滨或波鲁特先生等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许他就叫宫优斯达吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有人气的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…你们的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫三波春夫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.26,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.13,0:16:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是艺名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不可以再这样\N下次绝不可饶恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…那龙是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三犄龙，鸟盘目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与妈妈走失的小犄龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从辰已方位来的红恐龙被水弄湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.22,0:17:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下\N阳因阴而被一扫而去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而依旧活下来的龙\N本性是阳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，全都理解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理解什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学上的理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很低级的理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.83,0:17:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由此科学上的理解\N能得知此子的母亲的下落吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…得马上准备才行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成这小恐龙的妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，那是妈妈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.71,0:18:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊又来了，萨希家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.56,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你又想取小恐龙的命了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨…陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错…知道那陨石的目标\N是哪里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那恐龙之小孩…\N那红色即是目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何陨石会瞄准小恐龙落下呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.75,0:18:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石只不过是个石头而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.21,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.28,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐龙灭亡的原因\N据说是起因于巨大陨石的落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换言之\N那陨石足以毁灭整个世界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.89,0:18:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是此世界的小鬼吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希\N打击小鬼的任务就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.98,0:19:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.01,0:19:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令\N陨石停止降落！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石停下来\N拜托帮助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石别降落\N急急如律令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.26,0:19:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来阻止\N急急如律令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.64,0:19:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种非科学性的东西\N是无法解决问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还需要供品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.05,0:19:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,供品？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.39,0:19:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希，你随身携带之物\N何种最有价值呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.80,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手机吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个有价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.17,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信徒小步与萨希\N真诚地请求解除灾祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.81,0:20:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献上手机请求延续帝祚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，我们没死吧\N（那个人跑哪去了？）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希我们还活着哦\N（跑哪去了呀？）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们遇上大麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有供品是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错\N之前老是没给供品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是有价值的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个可以，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存在这世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.14,0:21:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有天尊神明与地尊神明啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.25,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存在这世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.52,0:21:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有天尊神明与地尊神明啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.73,0:21:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小犄龙，再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，感觉到城市的味道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:21:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这次有供品…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.68,0:23:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回的阿倍野…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.62,0:23:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对恐龙的了解\N真令我感到佩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.29,0:23:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？佩服吗？\N那没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.49,0:23:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有需要那么骄傲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.26,0:23:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是否对我另眼相看了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.49,0:23:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只认为个人有个人的专精知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.13,0:23:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不，小步若能那么做的话\N总有一天也能像我一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.00,0:24:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在现今的世界好像都是\N以你为中心而转动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.17,0:24:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，所以你别全做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.17,0:24:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样大家会更尊敬你的\N并且会更加喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.84,0:24:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要预告吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.57,0:24:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，由我来预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.81,0:24:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？下回？
